query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc mk t mi) NoMergeJoin(mc mi mk t ci) */ select count(*)
from title AS t
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 16
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.role_id = 2;
